# ============================================================================
# CODEOWNERS — file-level gate for high-blast-radius code paths (DM-R-2).
# ============================================================================
# Reference: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# Every PR that modifies a path below requires review from the listed owner(s).
# CODEOWNERS is ONLY enforced when "Require review from Code Owners" is enabled
# under Settings → Branches → Branch protection rules. Without that setting,
# this file is documentation, not a gate.
#
# Pair with:
#   - npm run migrations:verify    (DM-R-1 runtime barrier)
#   - .github/workflows/ci.yml     (DM-R-2 CI drift check)
# ============================================================================

# ---- Default owner — anything not claimed below. --------------------------
